d\">{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/jessi/chart-history/WDT|title=Jessi Chart History - World Digital Song Sales|website=Billboard.com|accessdate=October 15, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Life Is Good\" <small>(\uc778\uc0dd\uc740 \uc990\uac70\uc6cc)</small>\n| 2009 \n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| {{N/A}}\n| ''The Rebirth''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Unpretty Dreams\"\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 2015\n| 11 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n*KOR: 250,119<ref>Cumulative sales of \"Unpretty Dreams\":\n*{{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=S1020&targetTime=03&hitYear=2015&termGbn=month|title=2015\ub144 03\uc6d4 Download Chart|website=Gaon Music Chart|language=ko}}\n*{{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=S1020&targetTime=04&hitYear=2015&termGbn=month|title=2015\ub144 04\uc6d4 Download Chart|website=Gaon Music Chart|language=ko}}</ref>\n| ''[[Unpretty Rapstar discography#Unpretty Rapstar|Compilation Album Unpretty Rapstar Semi Final]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"I Want to Be Me\" <small>(\ub098\uc774\uace0 \uc2f6\uc5b4)</small>\n| 31 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n*KOR: 60,061<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=S1020&targetTime=04&hitYear=2015&termGbn=month|title=2015\ub144 04\uc6d4 Download Chart|website=Gaon Music Chart|language=ko}}</ref>\n|rowspan=\"5\" {{N/A|Non-album singles}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Ssenunni\" <small>(\uc388\uc5b8\ub2c8)</small>\n| 29 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n*KOR: 110,808<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=S1020&targetTime=09&hitYear=2015&termGbn=month|title=2015\ub144 09\uc6d4 Download Chart|website=Gaon Music Chart|language=ko}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Raise Your Heels\" <small>(\ub4b7\uafc8\uce58 \ub4e4\uc5b4)<br>(featuring [[Dok2]])</small>\n| 94 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n*KOR: 24,074<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gaonch