{"title_page": "Alfonso Martinez (actor)", "text_new": "{{Philippine name|Sumilang|Martinez}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name          = Alfonso Martinez\n| image         = \n| caption       = \n| birth_name     = Alfonso Sumilang Martinez\n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|mf=yes|1988|05|19}}\n| birth_place      = \n| othername     = Alfons Martinez\n| occupation    = Actor\n| years_active   = 1992\u2013present\n| homepage      = \n| notable role  = \n| parents = [[Albert Martinez]] (father)<br>[[Liezl Martinez]] (mother)\n}}\n\n'''Alfonso Sumilang Martinez''' is a [[Filipino people|Filipino]] actor. \n\n===Career===\nMartinez made his television debut, as Alfons Martinez, in [[ABS-CBN]]'s [[children's show|children]]'s gag-[[variety show]] [[Ang TV]].  He played a nephew to Aga Mulach, who is also his real-life maternal uncle, in the [[sitcom]] [[Oki Doki Doc]].<ref name=\"Comeback\"/>\n\nA month after [[Star Magic]] launched Star Magic Batch 15\u2014still in celebration of its 15th anniversary in 2007 -- [[ABS-CBN]]'s talent arm launched another batch of new talents. The group, dubbed as \"''Royalties''\", consisted of  [[Megan Young]], Gian Sotto, Michael Manahan, Michael Manotoc, Alfonso Martinez.<ref name=\"Royalties\"/>\n\nMartinez, along with [[Carl Guevarra]] joined the cast of [[Star Magic Presents]]:  [[Abt Ur Luv]] which was revamped to [[Abt Ur Luv|Abt Ur Luv, Ur Lyf 2]] in 2007.<REF name=\"AutoJV-1\"/> He played Daniel the romantic interest of [[Isabelle Abiera]]'s character in Abt Ur Luv Ur Lyf 2<REF name=\"Young Stars\"/>\u2014his first TV role in 15 years after his television debut in [[Ang TV]].\n\nWhen Abt Ur Luv Ur Lyf 2 ended in 2008, he then went to appear in 2 other seasons of Star Magic Presents namely: [[Astigs|Astigs in Haay...skul Lyf]] and [[Astigs|Star Magic Presents: Astigs in Luvin' Lyf]].<ref name=\"Lauren\"/><ref name=\"Camsur\"/>\n\n==Personal life==\n\nAlfonso Martinez is the eldest and only son of actors [[Albert Martinez]] and Liezl Martinez.<REF name=\"Comeback\"/><REF name=\"Royalties\"/><ref name=\"Oki 1\"/> He has two younger sisters Alynna and Alyssa. He is a paternal nephew of [[William Martinez (actor)|William Martinez]] and [[Yayo Aguila]] and is also a maternal nephew of actors [[Aga Muhlach]] and [[Charlene Gonzales]]. His maternal grandparents are actors [[Amalia Fuentes]] and [[Romeo Vasquez]].<ref name=\"Apo\"/>\n\nMartinez has scoliosis.<ref name=\"Scoliosis\"/>\n\n== Filmography ==\n\n=== Television ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" <!-- Do not center -->\n|- <!-- Never add unnecessary background colors -->\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes <!-- Do not replace with or add a Network/Channel column. Network rivalry is outside of Wikipedia. Do not replace with an Episode column, Notes column is not limited to episode titles. -->\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Source <!-- Use third party sources other than the actor's IMDB page -->\n|- <!-- Do not add rowspan -->\n| 1992-94\n| ''[[Ang TV]]''\n| Himself\n| Credited as \"''Alfons Martinez''\"\n| \n|-\n| 1993-94\n| ''[[Oki Doki Doc]]''\n| Fonzie\n| Credited as \"''Alfons Martinez''\"\n| <ref name=\"Oki 1\"/><ref name=\"Fonzie\"/> \n|-\n| 2007\n| ''[[Star Magic Presents]]:  [[Abt Ur Luv|Abt Ur Luv, Ur Lyf 2]]''\n| Daniel\n|\n|\n|-\n| 2008\n| ''[[Star Magic Presents]]:  [[Astigs|Astigs in Haay...skul Lyf]]''\n| Gibbs\n|\n| <ref name=\"Lauren\"/>\n|-\n| 2008\n| ''[[Star Magic Presents]]:  [[Astigs|Star Magic Presents: Astigs in Luvin' Lyf]]''\n| Marty\n|\n| <ref name=\"Camsur\"/>\n|-\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em|refs=\n\n<ref name=\"Apo\">{{cite web| url = https://www.manilatimes.net/2018/07/24/lifestyle-entertainment/show-times/albert-martinez-son-is-ulirang-apo/422635/ | title = Albert Martinez\u2019 Son is \u2018Ulirang Apo' | author = Carrasco, Ronnie | publisher = [[The Manila Times]] | date = 24 June 2018 | accessdate = 3 June 2014}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Camsur\">{{cite web| url = https://www.philstar.com/entertainment/2008/05/01/59329/astigs-braves-camsur-waters | title = Astigs Braves Camsur Waters | author = Glorioso, Bot | publisher = [[The Philippine Star]] | date = 1 May 2008 | accessdate = 3 June 2014}}</ref>\n\n <ref name=\"Scoliosis\">{{cite web | url =https://www.pep.ph/news/local/17685/alfonso-martinez-cannot-lose-much-weight-because-of-scoliosis | author = Erece, Dino | title = Alfonso Martinez Cannot Lose Much Weight Because of Scoliosis | publisher = pep.ph | date = 2008-05-30 | accessdate = 2009-01-27}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Lauren\">{{cite web | url =https://www.pep.ph/news/local/17685/alfonso-martinez-cannot-lose-much-weight-because-of-scoliosis | author = Plasencia, Von Daniel R. | title = Lauren Young, Empress Schuck Work Together in New Drama | publisher = Sun Star | date = 2019-02-22 | accessdate = 2020-01-27}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Oki 1\">{{cite web| url = https://news.abs-cbn.com/entertainment/05/19/09/eldest-son-celebrity-couple-turns-22 | title = Eldest Son of Celebrity Couple Turns 22 | publisher = ABS-CBN News | date = 19 May 2009 | accessdate = 3 June 2014}}</ref>\n\n <ref name=\"Fonzie\">{{cite web| url = https://tfc.tv/show/details/3558/oki-doki-doc | title = Oki Doki Doc | publisher = [[The Filipino Channel]] | date = 19 May 2009}}</ref>\n\n <ref name=\"Comeback\">{{cite web | url = http://www.pep.ph/features/extra/12940/new-star-magic-artist-alfonso-martinez-makes-showbiz-comeback | title = New Star Magic artist Alfonso Martinez makes showbiz comeback | author = Bonifacio, Julie | work = Features / Extra Extra | publisher = The Philippine Entertainment Portal | date = 2007-06-22 | accessdate = 2011-04-01}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Royalties\">{{cite web | url = http://www.pep.ph/news/13675/Star-Magic-launches- | title = Star Magic launches \"showbiz royalties\" | work = News | author = Erece, Dinno | publisher = The Philippine Entertainment Portal | date = 2007-06-18 | accessdate = 2011-04-01}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"AutoJV-1\">{{cite web | url =http://www.pep.ph/guide/1493/ABS-CBN-airs-new-youth-oriented-series-Astigs-starting-January-12 | author = Erece, Dino | title = ABS-CBN airs new youth-oriented show \"Astigs\" starting January 12 | work = Entertainment Guide - Television | publisher = Philippine Entertainment Portal | date = 2008-01-10 | accessdate = 2009-01-27}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Young Stars\">{{cite web | url = http://www.pep.ph/news/15014/Young-stars-come-and-go-in-ABS-CBN-teen-show- | title = Young stars come and go in ABS-CBN teen show \"Abt Ur Luv\" | author = Erece, Dinno | work = News | publisher = The Philippine Entertainment Portal | date = 2007-10-04 | accessdate = 2011-04-01}}</ref>\n\n}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Martinez, Alfonso}}\n[[Category:Star Magic]]\n[[Category:Star Magic Batch 15]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:1988 births]]\n\n\n{{Philippines-actor-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Philippine name|Sumilang|Martinez}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name          = Alfonso Martinez\n| image         = \n| caption       = \n| birth_name     = Alfonso Sumilang Martinez\n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|mf=yes|1988|05|19}}\n| birth_place      = \n| othername     = Alfons Martinez\n| occupation    = Actor\n| years_active   = 1992\u2013present\n| homepage      = \n| notable role  = \n| parents = [[Albert Martinez]] (father)<br>[[Liezl Martinez]] (mother)\n}}\n\n'''Alfonso Sumilang Martinez''' is a [[Filipino people|Filipino]] actor. \n\n===Career===\nMartinez made his television debut, as Alfons Martinez, in [[ABS-CBN]]'s [[children's show|children]]'s gag-[[variety show]] [[Ang TV]].  He played a nephew to Aga Mulach, who is also his real-life maternal uncle, in the [[sitcom]] [[Oki Doki Doc]].<ref name=\"Comeback\"/>\n\nA month after [[Star Magic]] launched Star Magic Batch 15\u2014still in celebration of its 15th anniversary in 2007 -- [[ABS-CBN]]'s talent arm launched another batch of new talents. The group, dubbed as \"''Royalties''\", consisted of  [[Megan Young]], Gian Sotto, Michael Manahan, Michael Manotoc, Alfonso Martinez.<ref name=\"Royalties\"/>\n\nMartinez, along with [[Carl Guevarra]] joined the cast of [[Star Magic Presents]]:  [[Abt Ur Luv]] which was revamped to [[Abt Ur Luv|Abt Ur Luv, Ur Lyf 2]] in 2007.<REF name=\"AutoJV-1\"/> He played Daniel the romantic interest of [[Isabelle Abiera]]'s character in Abt Ur Luv Ur Lyf 2<REF name=\"Young Stars\"/>\u2014his first TV role in 15 years after his television debut in [[Ang TV]].\n\nWhen Abt Ur Luv Ur Lyf 2 ended in 2008, he then went to appear in 2 other seasons of Star Magic Presents namely: [[Astigs|Astigs in Haay...skul Lyf]] and [[Astigs|Star Magic Presents: Astigs in Luvin' Lyf]].<ref name=\"Lauren\"/><ref name=\"Camsur\"/>\n\n==Personal life==\n\nAlfonso Martinez is the eldest and only son of actors [[Albert Martinez]] and Liezl Martinez.<REF name=\"Comeback\"/><REF name=\"Royalties\"/><ref name=\"Oki 1\"/> He has two younger sisters Alynna and Alyssa. He is a paternal nephew of [[William Martinez (actor)|William Martinez]] and [[Yayo Aguila]] and is also a maternal nephew of actors [[Aga Muhlach]] and [[Charlene Gonzales]]. His maternal grandparents are actors [[Amalia Fuentes]] and [[Romeo Vasquez]].<ref name=\"Apo\"/>\n\nMartinez has scoliosis.<ref name=\"Scoliosis\"/>\n\n== Filmography ==\n\n=== Television ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" <!-- Do not center -->\n|- <!-- Never add unnecessary background colors -->\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes <!-- Do not replace with or add a Network/Channel column. Network rivalry is outside of Wikipedia. Do not replace with an Episode column, Notes column is not limited to episode titles. -->\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Source <!-- Use third party sources other than the actor's IMDB page -->\n|- <!-- Do not add rowspan -->\n| 1992-94\n| ''[[Ang TV]]''\n| himself\n| Credited as \"''Alfons Martinez''\"\n| \n|-\n| 1993-94\n| ''[[Oki Doki Doc]]''\n| Fonzie\n| Credited as \"''Alfons Martinez''\"\n| <ref name